   "fieldname": "twitter_instructions",
   "fieldtype": "HTML",
   "options": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\"><strong>How to get X (Twitter) API Keys:</strong><ol><li>Go to <a href=\"https://developer.twitter.com/en/portal/dashboard\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter Developer Portal</a></li><li>Create a Project and App (or use existing)</li><li>In App Settings \u2192 Keys and Tokens:<ul><li><strong>OAuth 2.0:</strong> Copy Client ID and Client Secret</li><li><strong>OAuth 1.0a:</strong> Generate API Key and API Secret (needed for media uploads)</li></ul></li><li>In App Settings \u2192 User authentication settings:<ul><li>Enable OAuth 2.0</li><li>Type: Web App</li><li>Callback URL: <code>https://your-site.com/api/method/frappe_social.frappe_social.api.oauth.callback_twitter</code></li><li>Scopes: tweet.read, tweet.write, users.read, offline.access</li></ul></li></ol><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (17 posts/day), Basic $200/mo (100/day), Pro $5K/mo</div>"
